  "detailed_description": "<h1>DISCORD</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487060/extras/6b8b4c71c559c23b7f96d6f70d19e0dc.avif?t=1774542524\" width=600 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Join the Youtubers Life community</strong> on our official <strong>Discord</strong> server to stay up to date with all the latest news. Find out the first of the most special events, discover exclusive information and have fun with other players.</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487060/extras/a8df7d54811e64fd72c52571fab9398f.avif?t=1774542524\" width=600 height=136 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487060/extras/450651a6cda14c88b9973d9527cc3c79.avif?t=1774542524\" width=600 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487060/extras/ac36c1396dd04ccc64544637d2fcea36.poster.avif?t=1774542524\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487060/extras/ac36c1396dd04ccc64544637d2fcea36.webm?t=1774542524\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487060/extras/ac36c1396dd04ccc64544637d2fcea36.mp4?t=1774542524\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take your first step toward fame and <strong>experience 100% Youtubers Life</strong>, where every decision shapes your path. Start from scratch by creating VOD videos, sharing your best moments on Instalife, and overcoming challenges that will test your talent. Face off against rivals, gain followers, and prove you have what it takes to become <strong>the content creator you’ve always dreamed to be</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487060/extras/e5a8b9c43fd9897be3849a36348fa42e.avif?t=1774542524\" width=600 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487060/extras/b069a98b9947946f5c7daa936433b852.poster.avif?t=1774542524\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487060/extras/b069a98b9947946f5c7daa936433b852.webm?t=1774542524\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487060/extras/b069a98b9947946f5c7daa936433b852.mp4?t=1774542524\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It starts in an empty room and ends with a <strong>fully customized legendary house</strong> with a swimming pool, a cinema, your car collection and much more... <strong>Only you set the limit!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487060/extras/b62b2d6fb82a836ce0d9fd6e37415580.avif?t=1774542524\" width=600 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487060/extras/e851322bc223d0bdbb1aa5300b2aded6.poster.avif?t=1774542524\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487060/extras/e851322bc223d0bdbb1aa5300b2aded6.webm?t=1774542524\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487060/extras/e851322bc223d0bdbb1aa5300b2aded6.mp4?t=1774542524\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you want to climb fast in the rankings, <strong>don't forget to upgrade your PC</strong> and recording equipment, and buy new consoles to increase the results of your VODs. You can also hire employees: editors, financiers, or personal trainers <strong>to be more productive!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487060/extras/98f73010ff6b4a8561aca57bb7b73f76.avif?t=1774542524\" width=600 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487060/extras/30a52b83f7c4575c77b9c6edd0c6c898.poster.avif?t=1774542524\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487060/extras/30a52b83f7c4575c77b9c6edd0c6c898.webm?t=1774542524\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487060/extras/30a52b83f7c4575c77b9c6edd0c6c898.mp4?t=1774542524\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>When you become a popular star</strong>, the main brands will want you to be their image ambassador. Meet and negotiate with <strong>the most important companies of the moment</strong> and get the best possible conditions!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487060/extras/18a5821d472fbd35a054dfcdf319583e.avif?t=1774542524\" width=600 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487060/extras/a42c1874bb66e617ff6e64be4b03f7ff.poster.avif?t=1774542524\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487060/extras/a42c1874bb66e617ff6e64be4b03f7ff.webm?t=1774542524\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487060/extras/a42c1874bb66e617ff6e64be4b03f7ff.mp4?t=1774542524\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As your fame grows, you will be able to attend <strong>more and better events</strong>. Check your calendar and sign up for the ones you find most interesting. You'll be able to get <strong>unique items and interact with other youtubers from around the world</strong> to expand your network. Connect with other talents, make new friends, and who knows maybe something more... ;p</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487060/extras/a8df7d54811e64fd72c52571fab9398f.avif?t=1774542524\" width=600 height=136 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487060/extras/450651a6cda14c88b9973d9527cc3c79.avif?t=1774542524\" width=600 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487060/extras/ac36c1396dd04ccc64544637d2fcea36.poster.avif?t=1774542524\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487060/extras/ac36c1396dd04ccc64544637d2fcea36.webm?t=1774542524\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487060/extras/ac36c1396dd04ccc64544637d2fcea36.mp4?t=1774542524\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take your first step toward fame and <strong>experience 100% Youtubers Life</strong>, where every decision shapes your path. Start from scratch by creating VOD videos, sharing your best moments on Instalife, and overcoming challenges that will test your talent. Face off against rivals, gain followers, and prove you have what it takes to become <strong>the content creator you’ve always dreamed to be</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3487060/extras/e5a8b9c43fd9897be3849a36348fa42e.avif?t=1774542524\" width=600 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.ak